	‚Ä¢	Borrowing Base calculated monthly (eligible + ineligible + concentration adjustments)
	‚Ä¢	Advance rate cap of 80‚Äì90%
	‚Ä¢	Early Amortisation Triggers (MDCTA Schedule 10):
