	‚Ä¢	EV share: ‚â§ 25%
	‚Ä¢	Country concentration: ‚â§ 60%
	‚Ä¢	Utilisation ‚â§ Advance-Rate Cap
	‚Ä¢	OC targets: 31.1% (Class A), ~20% (Class B)
