‚ÄúPortfolio rotation remains robust, CTM at 6.3% above 5.0% floor, average days in inventory 109 (down MoM). No trigger breaches. OC continues to build, now 28.9% vs. 31.1% target. Liquidity reserve at 1.05% fully funded. Headroom to advance rate cap remains 2.1pp.‚Äù

